    educationalInfo: "Facts\n\n\u2022 Crabs help clean oceans by eating dead plants
      and animals.\n\u2022 They are important food for fish, birds, and turtles.\n\nAre
      they endangered?\n\nSome crab species are declining due to pollution, habitat
      loss (mangroves), and overfishing.\n\nProtection tips\n\n\u2022 Avoid littering
      on beaches \n\u2022 Protect mangrove forests\n\u2022 Do not collect crabs unnecessarily
